@database "Table column Guide"
@author "Heiko Schr—der"
@$VER: 3.0 (Release 3)
@wordwrap

@node Main "Table column V1.0"
                               @{" < Table of contents " link "Macro-Package.guide/Main"}

         !!! This Macro only works with £Final Writer 5¨ !!!

@{fg shine}Benifits:@{fg text}
   The Table manipulation is in FinalWriter very easy to get wrong and is
   therefore very uncomfortable. With this you can alter the column speci-
   fications much more easily and specifically.

@{fg shine}Requirements:@{fg text}
   £Final Writer 5¨ or later
   A Table ;-)

@{fg shine}Using the @{"macro" system "Sys:Utilities/Multiview TabColumn.iff"}:@{fg text}

   C@{fg fill}o@{fg text}lumn:
      Give the Nummber of the column to transform.
      With the Button right of field, you can get the information through ONE
      mouse click.

   @{fg fill}W@{fg text}idth:
      Set the width of the column in the above field.
      Warning: With FinalWriter the minimum column width must be 0.64cm.
               Anything smaller and Final Writer will not like it..

                     - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - - 

   @{fg fill}A@{fg text}pply
      The column will be altered to use the new figures.

   @{fg fill}C@{fg text}ancel
   @{fg fill}ESC@{fg text} or closing the window.
      Terminates the Macro.

@endnode
